dcterms:description: The Waymo Open Dataset contains 798 training sequences, 202 validation sequences, and 150 test sequences for vehicle, pedestrian, and cyclist detection. It is designed to facilitate the development and evaluation of 3D object detection algorithms.
dcterms:title: Waymo Open Dataset

dcterms:description: nuScenes is a multimodal dataset for autonomous driving that includes 700 training sequences, 150 validation sequences, and 150 test sequences, with annotations for 10 classes. The nuScenes detection score (NDS) is the main ranking metric for this dataset.
dcterms:title: nuScenes
